text.tspan: 7 PILLARS
Legacy Tech & Community Center
This center is the epicenter of our campus.
We will certify our people in technical and
medical trades so that they can earn a living
wage. The center will also serve as the HUB
for our community by providing before and
after school programs, STEM learning,
community kitchens and closets.
January 1st 2020 we will launch our very own online platform where you can
become a customer, seller, service provider or both! Its pretty simple, download
the Legacy App on your phone and purchase items or services from OUR
platform instead the others guys.
Our Mission
We have the belief system that the key to our future is that of self reliance and
economic independence. We must rebuild our communities to ensure that our
children are afforded all of the opportunities of other communities, we must join
together and redirect our spending. By making Legacy Brands your conscious
purchase you are ensuring that your dollar recirculates in our community and is
used to further our cause, Rebuilding Our Community, one purchase at a time.
Welcome to
ARE YOU READY TO MAKE
IMPACT IN OUR COMMUNITY?
With each dollar spent that you spent, 15% of total cost will be allocated to our
sister 501C3 Inspiring America. Inspiring America is a registered non-profit that
will support the 7 following pillars much needed in our community.
Legacy Markets
Our own grocery stories and corner stores
selling healthy foods.
Legacy Educational Fund
Our own fund that will provide scholarships for
our children and adults that are interested in
pursuing higher education. Part of the fund will
also assist in supporting our HBCUs.
Legacy M&D
We will manufacture and distribute not only our
own products but also create products that will
compete in the global market place. We must
return JOBS back to our community. This is the
only way we can change the paradigm of our
community.
Legacy Careers
We must ensure each member of our
community is given a proper career, vocational,
and educational advice to match passions and
skills to a suitable career. We will provide job
matching and staffing assistance to our
members.
Legacy Capital
The barrier to entry to become an entrepreneur
has long been out of reach for our members.
Legacy Capital will provide many services to
prepare our budding entrepreneurs in business
ownership. Moreover, we will provide mentors as
well as macro and micro loans to ensure that
their dreams come to fruition.
Legacy Properties
We will reclaim and revitalize our inner cities.
The once abandoned sectors will not become
bustling communities filled with apartments,
homes, business, mixed used develops, etc.
Legacy Careers
We must ensure that each member of our
community is given proper career, vocational,
and educational advice to match his/her
passions and skills to a suitable career. We will
provide job matching and staffing assistance to
our members
